Summary: 2 objects in SW sky aligned on top of one another.
divs: Sighting Detailswhile traveling west on i-80 in central iowa i looked to my southwest and saw 2 star like objects perpindicular to each other, looked somewhat odd, later i looked to sw and they were gone, object on bottom seem to be dimming in and out, object on bottom was larger and brighter.could not estimate distance.
